# Testing conventions

## Layout

| Project | Use for |
|---------|---------|
| `SampleCode` | Attribute definitions + decorated classes only (no generator ref) |
| `TestInfrastructure` | Compilation host, `TestEnvironment`, `[AttributeParser]` partials |
| `Tests` | TUnit coverage of runtime parser **and** generated partials |
| `Benchmarks` | Hot-path changes; keep `PreviousImplementation` for comparison |

## Adding behavior

1. Add/adjust fixtures under `SampleCode/TestAttributes` and `DecoratedClasses`
2. Expose generated parsers in TestInfrastructure when testing emit
3. Cover with TUnit via `TestEnvironment` / `ClassDataSource`
4. Prefer both raw `AttributeDataParser` and generated paths when changing emit

